reviewText: Increible, estoy en Buenos Aires, y en ninguna parte consigo esta pelicula, que es una de las mejores del cine Argentino, alguien sabe donde la puedo tener?

This is an essential film in the recent history of Argentina. The story is based on a real life case of kidnapping and torture of some youngsters (between 14-17) that were organized in various student associations that claimed some discounts to help the students.
